string.name: playAgain
string.comment: Appears as a button at the end of a tutorial chapter in a Lichess Study. This button lets you re-play the whole chapter.

string.name: whatWouldYouPlay
string.comment: Appear during tutorial chapters of a Lichess study. The user is asked to play a move and resolve the puzzle.

string.name: youCompletedThisLesson
string.comment: Appears at the end of a tutorial chapter in a study.

resources.string: శుభాకాంక్షలు! మీరు ఈ పాఠాన్ని పూర్తి చేసారు.
